This example somehow proceeds through synthesis when using the untimed method.
However, geometric catches the deadlock.
But this example has no timing information!
Here is a sample session, running first with untimed and then with geometric:

142 xia:~> cd ~peskin/atacs/examples/tel/
143 xia:examples/tel> ../../src/atacs -ltya dead
